  Ti7 Lam5 Thai3-peng5-iuN5 u7 chit8 e5 to2-su7 kio3-cho3 Ta-hi-ti. Ti7-hia e5 ia2-ban5 lang5 u7 liu5-thoan5 kong2 , Khi2-chhou cho7-hoa3 e5 sin5 theh8 ang5-thou5 cho3 chit8 e5 ta-pou-lang5. Kau3 chit8 jit8 chiong hit e5 lang5 ka7 i be5 hou7 i khun3--khi3, chiah tui3 hit e5 lang5 e5 seng-khu theh8 chit8 te3 kut-thau5 khi2-lai5 cho3 chit8 e5 cha-bou2-lang5. 
  Iu5-thai3 lang5 sou2 sin3-giong2 e5 kau3 si7 toa7-toa7 e7 thang hou7 se3-kai3 cho3 bou5-hoan7.In e5 keng-tian2 e5 lai7-bin7 ia7 u7 ki3-beng5 chhin-chhiuN7 chit-khoan2 e5 oe7.In kong2, siong7-te3 chhong3-cho7 thiN te7 ban7-mih8 i2-au7 , chiau3 I e5 heng5-siong7 e5 khoan2 iong7 thou5 chhong3-cho7 chit8-sian ang-a2.I chiu7 chiong I e5 khui3 pun5 jip8-khi3 hit sian ang-a2 e5 phiN7-khang, hit sian ang-a2 chiu7 oah8-khi2--lai5, kio3-cho3 A-tong, si7 ta-pou-lang5. Siong7-te3 chiu7 chiong A-tong chhong3 hou7 i khun3-khi3, chiong i e5 hiap8-kut theh8 chit8-ki khi2-lai5 cho3 chit8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5, kio3-cho3 ha7-oa.Che ia7 si7 chit8 cheng2 e5 liu5-thoan5.Chong2-si7 na7 chiau3 chit-khoan2 e5 kong2-hoat, kiam2 m7-si7 beng5-beng5 piau2-si7 lam5-chu2 si7 chu2, lu2-chu2 si7 chiong5.Lam5-chu2 khah kui3-khi3, lu2-chu2 khah ha7-chian7 mah?In-ui7 kong2 ta-pou-lang5 si7 tai7-seng u7, cha-bou2-lang5 si7 theh8 ta-pou-lang5 seng-khu e5 chit8-pou7-hun7-a2 lai5 cho3-chiaN5--e5. 
  Chhin-chhiuN7 chit-khoan2 e5 kong2-hoat kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 beh pian7-pok kong2, Kou2-cha2 e5 tai7-chi3 tai7-ke to long2 bo5 khak-sit8 e7 chai-iaN2.Chiau3 lan2 sou2 chai--e5 lai5 kong2, ta-pou-lang5 kiam2 m7-si7 long2 tui3 cha-bou2-lang5 e5 pak-tou2 nng3-chhut--lai5 mah?Sou2-i2 i beh kong2 lu2-chu2 si7 khah kui3-khi3, che khiok ia7 m7 si7 choan5-jian5 bo5 cheng5-li2. 
  Lan2 koh thiaN Lam5-iuN5 Ho5-chiu (Australia)e5 ou-sek lang5 kong2, Cho7-hoa3 e5 Chu2 kio3-cho3 Phan2-ji7, kiah8 i e5 to-a2 pak saN-tiuN e5 chhiu7-phoe5 chhu tiam3 thou5-kha, theh8 chit8-oan5 e5 liam5-thou5 khoa3-he7 hit teng2-bin7, cho3 nng7-sian ang-a2.I cho3 liau2 chin tek-i3, peh--khi2-lai5 thiau3-bu2 seh8 hit nng7-sian ang-a2 kui2-na7 lin3. I chiu7 koh pak chit8 khoan2 e5 chhiu7-phoe5, thiu-si liam5 tiam3 ang-a2 e5 thau5-khak, cho3 ang-a2 e5 thau5-mng5.I khoaN3-liau2 iu7 chin toa7 tek-i3.Koh tiam3 ang-a2 e5 chiu-ui5 thiau3-bu2 kui2-na7 lin3, chiong i e5 khui3 pun5 tui3 ang-a2 e5 phiN7-khang, pun5 chit8 toa7-e7 loh8-khi3, iah8 chiu7 koh thiau3 koh seh8.Lou7-boe2 chiong nng7-sian ang-a2 ian2-khi2-lai5 khia7, ang-a2 chiu7 soa3 chhio3 hi-hi, cho3-hoe2 kong2-oe7 chin chhin-bit8! 
  Tai7-ke sou2 chai, lan2 chit-peng5 kong2 lang5 si7 Po5-chia2-bo2 chhiok8-thou5 cho3-chiaN3--e5, chong2-si7 ta-pou cha-bou2 si7 an2-choaN2 hun-piat8 cho3, khiok si7 bo5 kong2-beng5 si7 siang7-si5 cho3--e5, m7-si7 tui3 ta-pou e5 seng-khu lai5 cho3-chhut cha-bou2-lang5;chit-tiam2 si7 beng5-pek8.Chiau3 teng2-bin7 chit nng7 khoan2 e5 liu5-thoan5 khoaN3, ta-pou cha-bou2 si7 siang7-si5 chiaN5--e5, khiok m7-si7 kong2 to2 chit8-peng5 khah tai7-seng.Tui3 an2-ni na2 chhin-chhiuN7 e7 iong7-tit kong2 m7-si7 ta-pou khah kui3-khi3, ia7 m7-si7 cha-bou2 khah ha7-chian7, si7 peng5-teng2 bo5 cheng-chha. 
  2. Chiong5-lai5 lu2-chu2 si7 hou7-lang5 khoaN3 chin khin 
  Teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2 si7 kui2 cham7 e5 chhio3-khoe-oe7 na7-tiaN7, si7 be7 chun2-pin5-tit.M7-ku2 na7 chiau3 lek8-su2 siong7 sit8-chai7 e5 su7-chek lai5 lun7, kau3 kin-a2-jit8 hu7-jin5-lang5 siu7 lang5 khoaN3-khin si7 chin-che7 lah.M7-si7 kong2 kan-ta to2 chit8 tah si7 an2-ni, choan5 se3-kai3 to long2 si7 chit8-iuN7. 
  Hian7-si5 chai7 Se-iuN5 tui3 lu2-chu2, pheng7 lan2 chit-peng5 si7 ke chin chun-tiong7.Chong2-si7 che si7 kin7-lai5 e5 tai7-chi3.Khah cha2 si7 kap lan2 bo5 cheng-chha.Lu2-chu2 e5 te7-ui7 pheng7 lam5-chu2 e5 si7 khah ke7 , si7 chha chin-che7.Lam5-chu2 si7 chu2, lu2-chu2 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 kin-sui5 e5 lang5.Khah kek8-toan e5 si5-tai7, ia7 bat khoaN3 lu2-chu2 cho3 chit8 cheng2 e5 chai5-san2, e7 iong7-tit chiau3 lam5-chu2 e5 i3-su3 ka7 i chhe-sai2 be2-be7, chhin-chhiuN7 be7 ti be7 iuN5 e5 khoan2-sit.Ia7 koh-chai3 khoaN3 lu2-chu2 cho3 kou2-goan2 ang-a2 e5 khoan2, thang hou7 lam5-chu2 thit-tho5 khoaN3-hong2. Koh-chai3 it-poaN si7 liah8 hu7-jin5-lang5 khoaN3-cho3 chin u-oe3, khoaN3-cho3 chhin-chhiuN7 iau-chiN e7 ham7-hai7 lang5 hoan7-choe7. 
  Chai7 Se3-kai3 e5 tiong-kan , Ki-tok-kau3 sng3-si7 te7-it chun-tiong7 lang5 e5 jin5-keh . Ia5-sou pun2-sin m7-na7 m7-bat kong2 hit ho7 khoaN3-khin hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 oe7, I tui3 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 thai3-tou7 sit8-chai7 si7 chin kong-peN5 . Sui-jian5 si7 an2-ni, au7-lai5 I e5 hak8-seng e5 lai7-te2 , u7 chit8 lang5 kio3-cho3 Po2-lo5; i si7 chin jiat8-sim chin gau5 chhian2-beng5 Ki-tok e5 ka3-si7 e5 toa7 su3-tou5. Chong2-si7 i bat kong2 , “Hu7-jin5-lang5 tioh8 ai3 tiam7-tiam7 hak8-sip8 to7-li2, tioh8 it-bi7 sun7-chiong5. Goa2 m7-chun2 hu7-jin5-lang5 kong2 to7-li2, ia7 m7-chun2 i koan2-hat ta-pou-lang5. I tioh8 kan-ta tiam7-tiam7 chiah ho2, in-ui7 A-tong si7 seng chhut-si3 , Ha7-oa si7 to3-boe2; koh-chai3 m7-si7 A-tong siu7 be5-hek8, si7 Ha7-oa siu7 be5 ham7-loh8 choe7.” Na7 kan-ta chiau3 chit ku3 oe7 khoaN3 , che beng5-beng5 si7 khoaN3 hu7-jin5-lang5 khah khin e5 cheng3-ku3. 
  Sin3 Put8-kau3 e5 lang5 khoaN3 hu7-jin5-lang5 si7 iau2-ku2 koh-khah m7-khi2 . M7-na7 pai3-put8 e5 lang5 si7 an2-ni, Put8-chou2 pun2-sin ia7-si7 khoaN3 hu7-jin5-lang5 m7 khi2. I khoaN3 hu7-jin5-lang5 kap ta-pou-lang5 tiong e5 phaiN2-lang5 tang5 chit8 teng2 ; kong2 in boe7 iong7-tit kap phou2-thong e5 ta-pou-lang5 tang5 chit8 khoan2 e5 ka3-si7; sou2-i2 tek8-piat8 siat chit8 cheng2 ha7-teng2 e5 ka3-si7, kio3-cho3 “Ha7-seng7 e5 Put8-kau3 , ” choan-choan teh ka3-si7 in chiah e5 ha7-teng2 e5 ta-pou-lang5 kap it-chhe3 e5 cha-bou2-lang5 ; ia7 i teh ka3 phou2-thong e5 ta-pou-lang5 chiu7 long2 iong7 khah siong7-teng2 e5 to7-li2, kio3-cho3 “Siong7-seng7 e5 Put8-kau3”. Put8-kau3 pun2-sin tui3 hu7-jin5-lang5 si7 i2-keng toa7-toa7 u7 bo5 kong-peN5 , sou2-i2 au7-lai5 hong7 i e5 ka3-si7 e5 lang5 si7 iau2 koh-khah koe3-thau5. In kong2 hu7-jin5-lang5 si7 u-oe3, ti3-kau3 hoe5-siuN7 bo5 chhoa7 bou2 ; iah8 kin3 hu7-jin5-lang5 be7 iong7-tit jip8 Put8-si7 pai3-put8. Chai7 Ju5-kau3 pai3 Khong2-chu2-kong e5 lang5 ia7 si7 u7 chit khoan2 e5 kian3-kai2 , kong2 hu7-jin5-lang5 be7 iong7-tit jip8 Seng3-bio7 che3-seng3. 
  U7 goa2 e5 peng5-iu2 , i beh chioh tiam5 Khong2-chu2 bio7-lai7 e5 Beng5-lun5-tong5, koa3 Khong2-chu2 e5 seng3-siong7 hap8-hun. Chin-che7 ku7-phai3 e5 lang5 tui3 chit chan5 hui-siong5 hoan2-tui3. In kong2 chhoa7 hu7-jin5-lang5 jip8 Seng3-bio7 si7 u-oe3--tioh8 Seng3-jin5. Sin-phai3 e5 lang5 thiaN-liau2 chin siu7-khi3; hiam2-hiam2 long7-chhut sin ku7 nng7-phai3 e5 toa7 chhiong-tut8 . Chiu7-si7 Khong2-chu2 pun2-sin ia7 u7 an2-ni kong2, ”I5 lu2-chu2 u2 siau2-jin5 ui5 lan5-iong2”（tok8-tok8 cha-bou2-lang5 kap bo5 tek-heng7 e5 lang5 choe3 te7-it oh khan-seng5 ）. Chit khoan2 kiam2 m7-si7 tui3 kin-te2 lai5 khoaN3-khin lu2-chu2 e5 kong2-hoat mah? 
  I2-cheng5 e5 tai7-chi3 chhiaN2 bo5 kong2 , chiau3 hian7-si5 chai7 lan2 e5 sia7-hoe7 , khoaN3 tang7 ta-pou, khoaN3-khin cha-bou2 e5 hong-khi3, iau2-ku2 si7 chin seng7. Lang5 na7 seN ta-pou-kiaN2 ka-ti7 ia7 chin tek-i3, chhin-chiaN5 peng5-iu2 ko3-ko3 moa2-chhui3 ka7 i kong2, “Kiong-hi2 !” Iah8 na7 seN cha-bou2-kiaN2 , chiu7 liah8 u7 chun2-cho3 bo5 e5 khoan2. Chhin-chiaN5 peng5-iu2 na7 u7 mng7 , in3 liau2 chiu7 khah bo5 lat8, bo5 siaN-boe2; mng7 e5 lang5 ia7 m7-kaN2 koh te7-ji7 ku3, liok8-liok8 kong2 chit8-ku3, “Ia7-ho2 !” chiu7 chun2 soah. Khah kek8-toan e5 lang5 na7 seN tioh8 cha-bou2-kiaN2, thoa--leh, chiu7 hou7--lang5 , na2 chhin-chhiuN7 tan3 chit8-te3 hau7-phiaN-phoe3 hiat-kak8 e5 khoan2-sit. 
  Chiong5-lai5 e5 lang5 kong2 , cho3 hu7-jin5-lang5 tioh8 u7 sam-chiong5 su3-tek chiah e7-iong7-tit chheng-cho3 ho2. Sim2-mih8 kio3-cho3 “Sam-chiong5” neh? Chiu7-si7 kong2, lu2-chu2 chit8-si3-lang5 e5 tiong-kan, tioh8 ai3 u7 saN-khoan2 e5 chiong5-sun7. Te7-it : iau2-boe7 chhut-ke3 e5 si5 tioh8 sun7-chiong5 lau7-pe7. Te7-ji7 : ke3-liau2 chiu7 tioh8 sun7-chiong5 tiong7-hu. Te7-saN: tiong7-hu si2-liau2 chiu7 tioh8 sun7-chiong5 i e5 kiaN2-ji5. Chit saN-cheng2 sun7-chiong5 e5 i3-su3, phah-sng3 kaN2 si7 choan chi2 kong2, hu7-jin5-lang5 it-seng tioh8 kap chit saN-khoan2 lang5 cho3-hoe2 koe3-jit8 seng-oah8, m7 eng-kai ka-ti7 khia7 tiam3 bo5 beng5-pek8 e5 sou2-chai7. Chong2-si7 phou2-thong e5 kai2-soat si7 kong2 cho3 hu7-jin5-lang5 hoan7-su7 m7 eng-kai ka-ti7 phah-sng3 , ka-ti7 m7-thang chip i3-kian3, tioh8 cho3 bo5 i3-kian3 e5 lang5; jim7-peng5 lau7-pe7 , tiong7-hu, kiaN2-ji5 e5 i3-su3, thoa--tioh8 m7-thang tun3-teN. Sou2-i2 siok8-gu2 u7 kong2, “Lu2-chu2 bo5-chai5 pian7 si7 tek.” Kong2 hu7-jin5-lang5 na7 bo5 chai5-cheng5 bo5 chu2-i3 chiu7-si7 e7-iong7-tit chheng-cho3 u7 ho2 tek-heng7. 
  Chit-khoan2 e5 sim-su kiam2 m7-si7 khoaN3 cha-bou2-lang5 cho3 si2-mih8, cho3 ki-khi3 teh khoan2-thai7 mah? Moa2-thiN-kha-e7 e5 chi2-moe7 m7-chai kheng2 jin7 an2-ni cho3 eng-kai, bo5? Na7 beh si7 m7-kheng2, chaiN2-iuN7 kui2-na7 chheng-ni5 i2-lai5 , chiau3 su7-sit8 khoaN3, chi2-moe7 thai3 long2 hou7 lang5 khoaN3 chin khin, tit8-tit8 soa3 kau3 kin-a2-jit8 neh? Chit tiong-kan e5 ui2-khiok goa2 hi-bong7 cheng3 chi2-moe7 tioh8 chhim-chhim ka-ti7 hoan2-seng2 khoaN3. 
  3. Lu2-chu2 chaiN2-iuN7 hou7 lang5 khoaN3 khin neh? 
  Chiau3 goa2 khoaN3 lu2-chu2 siu7 lam5-chu2 khoaN3-khin e5 li2-iu5 u7 saN-hang7: 
  Te7-it, in-ui7 lang5 e5 to7-tek-sim bo5 hoat-tat8 , kou3 ka-ti7 bo5 kou3 pat8-lang5 , tiong7 su-iok8 bo5 tiong7 kong-li2; siuN7 theh8-jip8 siuN7 pa3-chiam3 , bo5 siuN7 theh8-chhut kap lang5 pun. Tui3 an2-ni khoaN3 lang5 e5 seN3-mia7 chhin-chhiuN7 chiau2-mng5 hiah khin, khoaN3 ka-ti7 e5 seN3-mia7 chhin-chhiuN7 Thai3-san hiah tang7, long2 be7-hiau2 sio the2-thiap; kiong5 chiah8 jiok8, u7 lat8--e5 khia7-thau5 tian2-ui; loan2-jiok8--e5 chiu7 tioh8 thun-lun2 hok8-chiong5, siu7 lang5 hou-hat. Lu2-chu2 goan5-lai5 e5 seN-cho3 kap lam5-chu2 toa7-toa7 bo5 sio-siang7. I e5 sin-chai5 khah sio2-se3, iah8 chit8-goeh8-jit8 ai3 chit8 pai2 e5 bo5 chu7-iu5 ; i e5 ku2-chi2 khah iu3-siu3, kin-kut khah bo5 lat8. Sou2-i2 chai7 hit ho7 bo5 to7-tek, phin2 khui3-lat8 phin2 iong2 e5 si5-tai7, lu2-chu2 tioh8 niu7 lam5-chu2 saN-pou7, tioh8 siu7 hou-hat, che si7 khoai3-siuN7 e5 tai7-chi3. 
  Te7-ji7 e5 li2-iu5 si7 in-ui7 gin2-na2 to long2 si7 tui3 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 pak-tou2 nng3--chhut-lai5; koh-chai3 gin2-na2 tioh8 chiah8 i e5 leng chiah e7 oah8, put-si5 to be7 iong7-tit li7-khui i. Tui3 an2-ni bo2-kiaN2 e5 ai3-cheng5 si7 pi2 pe7-kiaN2 khah chhim. Hu7-jin5-lang5 sui-si7 siu7 lam5-chu2 e5 khoaN3-khin phaiN2 khoan2-thai7, ui7-tioh8 thiaN3 kiaN2 e5 ian5-kou3, ban7-su7 long2 thun-lun2. Ta-pou-lang5 chai-iaN2 hu7-jin5-lang5 u7 siu7 ai3-cheng5 sok-pak8, tui3 an2-ni chiu7 soa3 ju2 kho3-siok8 ju2 hong3-su3. 
  Te7-saN e5 li2-iu5 si7 chai7 hu7-jin5-lang5 pi2 ta-pou-lang5 khah bo5 kau3-iong2 , khah bo5 chai5-cheng5 , chit-tiam2 si7 hu7-jin5-lang5 siu7 ta-pou-lang5 kheng-si7 choe3 toa7 e5 goan5-in. Lu2-chu2 pheng7 lam5-chu2 , u7 thang siu7 kau3-iong2 e5 ki-hoe7 si7 ke chin chio2. Chiau3 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2, lu2-chu2 e5 sin-the2 siong5-siong5 e7 m7 tu2-ho2 , koh-chai3 i tioh8 iuN2-chhi7 kiaN2-ji5, che7-che7 be7 thang chiau3 i3-su3. M7-na7 an2-ni, lam5-chu2 ui7-tioh8 ai3 hong3-hu3 koan2-hat hu7-jin5-lang5 , i bo5 ai3 hu7-jin5-lang5 kap i peN5-peN5 gau5; sou2-i2 m7-na7 bo5 chiong2-le7 lu2-chu2 thak8-chheh siu7 kau3-iong2, hoan2-tng2 chou2-tong3 hu7-jin5-lang5 ai3 hak8-bun7 e5 sim si7 khah che7. 
  U7 siat to7-tek hou7 lu2-chu2 siu2, kio3 i tioh8 u7 sam-chiong5 su3-tek chiah ho2; ban7-su7 tioh8 sun7-chiong5 ta-pou-lang5, m7-thang su-khia u7 chu2-i3; sou2-i2 m7-bian2 bat sim2-mih8 hak8-bun7, kan-ta gau5 khoan2-thai7 ta-pou-lang5 chiu7 ho2. Ti3-kau3 hu7-jin5-lang5 ka-ti7 ia7 soa3 sip8-i2 ui5-siong5 , bo5 siuN7 beh chin3-pou7, beh kap ta-pou-lang5 siang7 khoan2, chin-chiaN3 soa3 sin3, kong2, “Lu2-chu2 bo5 chai5, pian7 si7 tek;” sin3 chit-ku3 si7 chin-li2 , it-chhe3 e5 hak8-bun7 long2 pang3 hou7 lam5-chu2 khi3 oh8, ban7-hang7 e5 kang-ge7 ia7 it-chin7 jim7-pin5 ta-pou-lang5 khi3 tit. 
  Kau3-boe2 hu7-jin5-lang5 soa3 piN3-cho3 chit8-chiong2 bo5 chi3-khi3 e5 mih8, kan-ta e7-hiau2 chng sui2. ng3-bang7 tit-tioh8 ta-pou-lang5 e5 lin5-bin2; sit8-chai7 thau5-khak-oaN2-lai7 khang-lo-so, m7-bat hoaN5-tit8; tu5-khi3 chu2-chiah8 , pou2-thiN7 , se2-sau3 i2-goa7, to bo5 u7 khah kian3-tiong5 e5 sou2-chai7. Tui3 an2-ni khoaN3, lu2-chu2 ka-ti7 be7 thang cho3 sim2-mih8; na7 m7-si7 oa2-kho3 ta-pou-lang5 e5 ti3-im3 , ka-ti7 be7 thang oah8. Be7 thang tok8-lip8 seng-oah8 e5 lang5 , m7-bian2 kong2 si7 lu2-chu2, chiu7-si7 lam5-chu2 ia7 si7 tek-khak hou7 lang5 khoaN3-khin lah! 
  Lu2-chu2 siu7 lam7-chu2 khoaN3-khin e5 li2-iu5 i2-goa7 khiok si7 iau2 u7, chong2-si7 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2 chit saN-tiam2 si7 choe3 chu2-iau3, Si5-se3 i2-keng pian3-oaN7 liau2 , kok-hang7 tai7-chi3 to long2 kap cheng5 toa7-toa7 u7 cheng-chha, chiu7-si7 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 te7-ui7 ia7 i2-keng koan5 chin-che7 . Chai7 Se-iuN5 lu2-chu2 kap lam5-chu2 e5 te7-ui7 si7 chha-put-to kau3 beh peN5-peN5 . Tian-to3 u7 sou2-chai7 lu2-chu2 e5 te7-ui7 khah koan5 e5 ia7 si7 u7. Iah8 e7 ti3-kau3 an2-ni e5 goan5-in , bo5 pat8-hang7 , chiu7-si7 in-ui7 si5-se3 e5 chin3-pou7 ; lang5 e5 to7-tek-sim u7 khah koan5, e7-hiau2 chun-tiong7 lang5 e5 jin5-keh, ti3-kau3 m7-kaN2 ui7-tioh8 lu2-chu2 loan2-jiok8 chiu7 khoaN3-khin i. Chong2-si7 choe3 toa7 e5 goan5-in, choe3 tit8-chiap e5 li2-iu5 , si7 in-ui7 hu7-jin5-lang5 ka-ti7 u7 chu7-kak, m7-goan7 put-si5 khia7 lang5 e5 boe2-au7, kian3-siau3 put-si5 siu7 lam5-chu2 e5 ti3-im3 , ka-ti7 siuN7 chin3-pou7 hun3-hoat bian2-kiong2; put-lun7 thak8-chheh, hek8-si7 cho3 kang, long2 bo5 beh su ta-pou-lang5 . Chit-tiam2 choe3 u7 koan-he7, choe3 iau3-kin2. 
