  Khi2-chhou gin2-na2 ti7 lau7-bo2 e5 pak-tou2-lai7 e5 si5, sit8-chai7 hit-si5 si7 nng7-lang5 sio-kap chit8-tiau5 seN3-mia7. Thang kong2 lau7-bo2 e5 sim chiu7-si7 kiaN2 e5 sim, lau7-bo2 e5 bah chiu7-si7 kiaN2 e5 bah. Sou2-i2 hit e5 si5-chun7 cho3 lau7-bo2 e5 lang5 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 , chi2-moe7 tai7-ke m7-chai u7 beng5-pek8 bo5? Gin2-na2 chhut-si3 liau2 choe3 u7 koan-he7--e5 si7 lau7-bo2 e5 leng. Lin2 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 kou3 hou7 leng ho2, iah8 chit8 jit8 tioh8 hou7 i chiah8 kui3-pai2, chi2-moe7 m7-chai u7 gian2-kiu3 a2-bo5? 
  Chiau3 goa2 sou2 khoaN3 hian7-si5 e5 chi2-moe7 khah che7 kan-ta e7-hiau2 seN , be7-hiau2 chhi7. Gin2-na2 e5 sim-li2 , khoeh-khiam3 , gin2-na2 u7 iau, u7 koaN5 a2-bo5, be7-hiau2-tit e5 si7 khah toa7 pou7-hun7. Lan2 e5 gin2-na2 in-ui7 iuN2-chhi7 e5 lang5 be7-hiau2-tit, ti3-kau3 lai5 si2-sit e5 si7 chin che7. Chai7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 Pun2-to2-lang5 chiau3 Tai7-cheng3 11 ni5 e5 tiau-cha, chit8-ni5 si2 chha-put-to u7 9,5000 lang5. Chiong5-tiong chit8-hoe3 kau3 gou7-hoe3 e5 gin2-na2 chiam3 beh kau3 tui3-poaN3 , si7 chiong-kin7 4,4000 lang5. Chit 4,4000 e5 si2 gin2-na2 e5 lai7-te2, kau3 chit8-hoe3 teh chiah8-ni e5, chiam3 chha-put-to 2,7000 lang5. Li2 siuN7, kiam2 m7-si7 chin thang ai3 tioh8 kiaN? Che long2 si7 in-ui7 iuN2-chhi7 m7 tu2-ho2 sou2 tai3 lai5--e5 chhi-chham2 lah. 
  Lu2-chu2 m7-na7 tioh8 cho3 gin2-na2 e5 lau7-bo2 , iau2-ku2 tioh8 cho3 gin2-na2 e5 sian-seN. Gin2-na2 iau2-boe7 jip8 hak8-hau7 e5 tiong-kan, ban7-hang7 to si7 pai3 lau7-bo2 cho3 sian-seN, tui3 lau7-bo2 oh8. M7-na7 si7 tui3 lau7-bo2 oh8 kong2-oe7, chit8-si3-lang5 e5 seng3-cheng5 siu7 lau7-bo2 e5 kam2-hoa3 si7 hui siong5 toa7. Jit8-pun2 Loe7-te7 u7 chit8-ku3 siok8-gu2 kong2, “SaN-hoe3 gin2-na2 e5 cheng-sin5 soa3 kau3 chit8-pah hoe3.” Se-iuN5 ia7 u7 siok8-gu2 kong2, “Io5 io5-na5 e5 chhiu2 e7 thang io5-tang7 thiN-kha-e7.” Chit-khoan2 oe7 long2 si7 chheng-chan3 lu2-chu2 e5 toa7 khui3-lat8, chi2-beng5 lau7-bo2 tui3 gin2-na2 e5 kam2-hoa3 si7 chhim koh toa7. Lan2 na7 khoaN3 lek8-su2 sou2 ki3-chai3 e5 eng-hiong5, toa7 gau5-lang5 sou2 cho3 e5 tai7-chi3 , koh-chai3 khe-kho2 hiah e5 lang5 e5 lau7-bo2 e5 chai5-cheng5 tek-heng7 kap tui3 i e5 kiaN2 e5 iong7-sim, lan2 chiu7 chiok-giah8 e7 thang beng5-pek8 lau7-bo2 tui3 gin2-na2 e5 kam2-hoa3 u7 loa7-toa7, cho3 lau7-bo2 e5 chek-seng5 si7 loa7-tang7 neh? Sou2-i2 goa2 kong2 e7 seN-kiaN2 be7-e7 ka3-kiaN2, si7 bo5 koh-iuN7 e7-hiau2 chai-hoe be7-hiau2 ak-chui2; e7-hiau2 pou3-tiu7 be7-hiau2 ban2-chhau2. Chit cheng2 hu7-jin5-lang5 be7-kham-tit cho3 gin2-na2 e5 lau7-bo2, chi2-ho2 cho3 ke-a2-kiaN2 e5 ke-bo2. SeN-kiaN2 si7 chin oh, iuN2-kiaN2 koh-khah oh, chong2-si7 ka3-kiaN2 si7 iau2-ku2 koh-khah oh! 
  Hu7-jin5-lang5 beh chin7 iuN2-chhi7 kiaN2-ji5 e5 pun2-hun7, i tioh8 koh chu3-i3 chit8 hang7. Chit-hang7 si7 lan2 chio2-chio2 siuN7 u7 kau3 e5 tai7-chi3 . Lan2 e5 lang5 m7-na7 tui3 hoe3-siu7 chiN5-chai5 u7 tham-sim, tui3 kiaN2-ji5 ia7 si7 to-to ek-sian7, long2 bo5 hiam5. Lun7 seN-kiaN2 e5 su7 khiok si7 cho3 lang5 e5 toa7 pun2-hun7, lang5-lang5 to tioh8 u7. 
