  Li2 khoaN3 : chai7 lan2 tiong-kan chit-khoan2 bo5 chek-seng5 e5 lau7-pe7 lau7-bo2 kiam2 chio2-chio2 mah? Tai7-ke tioh8 ai3 chai, ke seN chit8 e5 bo5 ka3-si7 e5 gin2-na2 , si7 ke pang3 chit8 taN3 tang7-taN3 hou7 cheng3-lang5 taN , kiam2-chhai2 si7 ke pang3 chit8 chiah8 hou2 ka7 lang5. Sou2-i2 seN-kiaN2 si7 ho2, si7 chin thang kiong-hi2 ; chong2-si7 ia7 tioh8 chun2-chat, e7-hiau2 liong7 khui3-lat8 , e7 seN-kiaN2 ia7 tioh8 e7 khan-seng5 kiaN2 chiah ho2. na7 bo5 liong7 khui3-lat8 , loan7-loan7 seN, kau3-boe2 tioh8 pang3 teh ku3-chai7 i , che m7-na7 si7 hai7 kiaN2-ji5, hai7 sia7-hoe7 si7 chin che7. 
  Lu2-chu2 te7-ji7 e5 thian-chit si7 liau7-li2 ka-su7. Lam5-chu2 na7 pi2-pheng7 cho3 chiong3-kun, lu2-chu2 chiu7-si7 siong3-ia5. Chiong3-kun si7 choan-chu2 kou3 goa7-bin7 , siong3-ia5 si7 choan-chu2 li2 lai7-bin7. Koh-chai3 tui3 liau7-li2 ka-su7 chit-tiam2 kong2 , lu2-chu2 si7 ka-teng5 lai7 e5 ong5, in-ui7 ka-teng5 lai7-bin7 e5 tai7-chi3 eng-kai long2-chong2 tioh8 ai3 i chiang2-koan2. 
  Teng2-cham7 u7 kong2 Se-iuN5 lu2-chu2 e5 te7-ui7 put-chi2 koan5, put-pi2 lan2 chit-peng5, in chin siu7 lam5-chu2 e5 chun-keng3. Che si7 u7 chiong2-chiong2 e5 goan5-in . Se-iuN5 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 tui3 liau7-li2 ka-su7 chit-chan5 sit8-chai7 chin giam2-nge7; in long2 goan5-choan5 , m7-bian2 ta-pou-lang5 chhap-chhui3 , pan7-li2 chap8-hun chiu-chi3 kau3-kak. Se-iuN5 e5 lu2-chu2 sit8-chai7 oan5-choan5 si7 ka-teng5 e5 lu2-ong5, choan5-pou7 e5 ka-su7 long2 si7 in chu2-chiang2. Ta-pou-lang5 tui3 goa7-bin7 tng2-lai5, giam2-jian5 chhin-chhiuN7 cho3 lang5-kheh, si7 kan-ta siu7 an-ui3 hiong2-hok na7-tiaN7 . Ti7 goa7-bin7 siu7 hong-song, tng2-lai5 kau3 chhu3-mng5-khau2, chiu7 u7 leng2-li7 chhio3-hi-hi e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 ti7-hia tan2-hau7 i; i kan-ta chiong i ti7 goa7-bin7 phah-piaN3 sou2 tit--e5 theh8 kau hu7-jin5-lang5 , i2-goa7 i ti7 chhu3-lai7 kan-ta thi2-khui-chhui3 chiah8-png7 chiu7 ho2, m7-bian2 hoan5-lo2 bi2-ke3 koan5 a2-si7 ke7. Iah8 i kan-ta teh che7, ha sio-te5, thau5 khi-khi khoaN3 chheng-hiu u7 cheng2-tun3 e5 chhu3 lai7-bin7 ; pho7 i e5 oah8-tang7 kek8 khiau2-khi3 u7 kui-ki2 e5 hau7-seN cha-bou2-kiaN2; thiaN in liam7 “Goeh8 kong-kong, siu3-chai5 long5, khia5 peh8-be2 koe3 lam5-tong5......” Hit khoan2 e5 gin2-na2 koa, hek8-si7 thiaN i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 po3-ko3 chhin-chhek ong2-lai5 e5 siau-sit, peng5-iu2 e5 phoe-sin3. A2-si7 i ti7 goa7-bin7 sou2-cho3 be7 tiau5-tit8 e5 tai7-chi3, chiu7 kong2 lai5 kap i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 chham-siong5, thiaN hu7-jin5-lang5 khin-siaN se3-soeh e5 khoan2-khng3, se2-khi3 i sim-lai7 e5 ut-chut. 
  U7-tang-si5 hong-chheng jit8-loan2 e5 si5 ang-bou2 sio-khan a2-si5 chhoa7 kiaN2 khi3 kong-hng5 kiaN5-soa2, hek8-si7 khi3 ia2-goa7 khoaN3 keng2-ti3. U7-tang-si5 goeh8-kng, chheN-beng5 e5 si5-chun7 , ang chiu7 toaN5, bou2 chiu7 chhiuN3 , kiaN2-ji5 chiu7 thiau3-bu2, sio-kap chheng-chan3 jin5-seng e5 ho5-lok8, kam2-sia7 ka-teng5 e5 hok-khi3. Ta-pou-lang5 sou2 siu7 e5 hong-tin5 , thang kong2 chit8-pai2 tng2-lai5 kau3 chhu3-lai7, in-ui7 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 iong7-sim long2-chong2 se2 chheng-khi3. M7-na7 an2-ni , iau2-ku2 si7 ke-tit pah-poe7 e5 iong2-khi3 thang chhut-khi3 sia7-hoe7 toa7 tin2-tang7. Ah! Se-iuN5-lang5 e7 u7 kin-a2-jit8 , kiam2 long2 si7 ta-pou-lang5 gau5--e5 mah? 
  Cheng3 chi2-moe7 hiaN-ti7 , Se-iuN5 lang5 khoaN3 i e5 ka-teng5 chhin-chhiuN7 Thian-tong5 , chhin-chhiuN7 Se-thian kek8-lok8 e5 sou2-chai7. Iah8 hian7-si5 lan2 e5 ka-teng5 khah-che7 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 sim2-mih8 khoan2? Kiam2 m7-si7 chhin-chhiuN7 kaN-gak8 a2-si7 te7-gek8--e5 si7 khah toa7 pou7-hun7? Tui3 bak8-chiu sou2 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 kong2 , chai7 lan2 e5 ka-teng5 ta-pou-lang5 khah-che7 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 ong5-ia5-kong, hu7-jin5-lang5 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 cha-bou2-kan2. Thang kong2 lan2 e5 ka-teng5 si7 lam5-chu2 choan-che3 e5 kok-tou7. Liat8-ui7 , lan2 e5 sia7-hoe7 si7 chin bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 lang5 , chong2-si7 lan2 tioh8 chai, lan2 e5 ka-teng5 si7 iau2 khah m7-chiaN5-mih8. Lan2 e5 sia7-hoe7 soe-the3 e5 goan5-in che7-che7 si7 tui3 lan2 e5 ka-teng5 hu2-pai7 sou2 ti3--lai5 e5 lah! HiaN-ti7 chit-tiam2 lin2 u7 tong5-i3, bo5? Chi2-moe7 lin2 u7 seng5-jin7, bo5? 
